from dev_work.crw_ae_tax_registrations_d_mw_20200318
where ird_number = 44745151
and tax_type = 'GST'
order by record_effective_timestamp

select case when act.account_halt_flag = 'Y' and expd_halt_level_indicator <> 'X' and expd_halt_level_indicator is not NULL then 'account_halt_flag Y is as expected (not NULL) - OK'
         when act.account_halt_flag = 'N' and expd_halt_level_indicator = 'X' and expd_halt_level_indicator is not NULL then 'account_halt_flag N is as expected (X) - OK'
         else 'account_halt_flag may not be as expected - CHECK!!' end chk, 
    act.*, expd.ird_number, expd.location_number, expd.tax_type, expd.expd_halt_level_indicator, expd.timeline_start_final expd_timeline_start, expd.timeline_end_final expd_timeline_end
from (
    select * from test_staging.md_test_ACCOUNT_act_acct_halt_flag_edw
    where account_ird_number = '010011590'
    ) act
full outer join (
    select * from test_staging.md_test_ACCOUNT_exp_acct_halt_flag_edw aa
    where exists (select 1 from test_staging.md_test_ACCOUNT_act_acct_halt_flag_edw bb
        where aa.ird_number = cast(bb.account_ird_number as int)
        and aa.location_number = cast(bb.heritage_location_number as int)
        and case when bb.account_type_code in ('IIT', 'ITN') then 'INC' 
            when bb.account_type_code = 'PSO' then 'PAY' 
            else bb.account_type_code end  
                = aa.tax_type 
        )
    and ird_number = 10011590
    ) expd
on cast(act.account_ird_number as int) = expd.ird_number
and cast(act.heritage_location_number as int) = expd.location_number
and case when act.account_type_code in ('IIT', 'ITN') then 'INC' 
         when act.account_type_code = 'PSO' then 'PAY' 
         else act.account_type_code end  
         = expd.tax_type 
and act.timeline_end_final = expd.timeline_end_final

select a.from_ird_number as group_id, b.to_ird_number as ird_number, a.fstrlinktype as link_type, a.nbr as nbr_links, c.net_group_position
from
(select a.from_ird_number, a.fstrlinktype, count(distinct a.to_ird_number) as nbr
from tmp_assoc_ent_all a
join lab_gst_project.decision_gst_backup b
 on a.to_ird_number=b.ird_number
where a.relationship_active='Y'
group by from_ird_number, fstrlinktype) a
join tmp_assoc_ent_all b
 on a.from_ird_number = b.from_ird_number
  and b.relationship_active='Y'
join 
(select a.from_ird_number, sum(a.dm_tax_position) as net_group_position
from
(select distinct a.from_ird_number, a.to_ird_number, b.dm_tax_position
from tmp_assoc_ent_all a
join lab_gst_project.decision_gst_backup b
 on a.to_ird_number=b.ird_number
where a.relationship_active='Y'
 and a.from_ird_number=93824615) a
group by from_ird_number) c
 on a.from_ird_number = c.from_ird_number
where a.nbr > 1
 and a.from_ird_number=93824615

create table lab_r3_assurance_project.tmp_employmer_records
          stored as parquet as 
          select
                    rollup.flngcustomerkey
                    , rollup.flngaccountkey
                    , rollup.fdtmfilingperiod
                    , rollup.fstrlistformataddress
                    , count(rollup.fdtmfilingperiod) as fintemployeecount /*count of all employees included on returns for filing period */
                    , sum(fblnactiveemployee) as fintactiveemployeecount /*count of all employees with non-zero income for the filing period*/
              from  (select * 
                    from lab_r3_assurance_project.all_employees
                    where fstrirdnumber = '000000000'
                                        union 
                    
                               /*select records with a non-zero IRD number, grouped at an ird-number level to ignore any name variations*/
                    select flngcustomerkey
                               , flngaccountkey
                               , fstrlistformataddress
                               , fdtmfilingperiod
                               
                               , min(fstremployeename)
                               , fstrirdnumber
                               , max(fblnactiveemployee)
                    from lab_r3_assurance_project.all_employees where fstrirdnumber != '000000000'
                    
                    group by flngcustomerkey
                               , flngaccountkey
                               , fdtmfilingperiod
                               , fstrirdnumber
                               , fstrlistformataddress
                    
                               ) rollup
               group by flngcustomerkey, flngaccountkey, fdtmfilingperiod, fstrlistformataddress

create table lab_r3_assurance_project.tmp_employees
stored as parquet as
select --distinct
                                                     
                                                     
                                                    
                                                      Employees.fstrirdnumber as EMPLOYEE_IRD_NUMBER
                                                     --, customer.fstrlistformatname as EMPLOYEE_NAME
                                                     --, customer.fstrlistformataddress as EMPLOYEE_ADDRESS
                                                     --, from_timestamp(employer.party_start_date, 'dd/MM/yyyy') as Emplyee_DOB
                                                     , customer.fstrzip as EMPLOYEE_POST_CODE
                                                     , employer.ird_number as EMPLOYER_IRD_NUMBER
                                                     --, customer.fstrtitle as EMPLOYEE_TITLE
                                                     --, concat(nvl(customer.fstrfirstname, ''), ' ', nvl(customer.fstrmiddlename, '')) as employee_first_names
                                                     --, customer.fstrfamilyname as EMPLOYEE_SURNAME
                                                     , case when sum(employees.fcurgross) > 0 then 'Y' else 'N' end as Employee_paid
                                                     --, case when countemp.employee_multiple_employers > 1 then 'Y' else 'N' end as employee_multiple_employers
                                                     
                                                     
                          
                                           from prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblnz_rtnpsoemployeeinfo Employees
                          
                                           inner join prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblreturn Return
                                                     on Employees.flngreturnkey = Return.flngreturnkey
                                                     and Return.record_active_flag = 'Y'
                                                     and Return.fstrreason is null /*this field will be populated for removed/duplicate returns*/
                                           inner join lab_r3_assurance_project.tmp_latest_return latest
                                           on Return.flngaccountkey = latest.flngaccountkey
                                           and return.fdtmfilingperiod = latest.fdtmfilingperiod 
                                           inner join prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblcustomerinfo customer
                                           on employees.fstrirdnumber = customer.fstrid
                                           and customer.record_active_flag = 'Y'
                                           and customer.flngcustomerkey != 0
                                           inner join prod_refined_restricted_access.party_dim employer
                                           on latest.flngcustomerkey = cast(employer.customer_key as int)
                                           and employer.record_active_flag = 'Y'
                                           inner join 
                                           (select count (fstrirdnumber) as employee_multiple_employers, fstrirdnumber
                                            from (select distinct fstrirdnumber, flngaccountkey, fdtmfilingperiod
                                            from lab_r3_assurance_project.tmp_latest_period_emp) a
                                            group by fstrirdnumber
                                            ) countemp
                                           on customer.fstrid = countemp.fstrirdnumber
                                           
                                           left join prod_refined_restricted_access.organisation_dim charities
                                            on employer.customer_key = charities.customer_key
                                            and charities.record_active_flag = 'Y'
                                            --and (charities.charity_org_flag = 'Y'
                                            and charities.party_subtype in ('Government Department', 'Public Authority (Govt)')
                                            
                                           
                                           
                                           where Return.fdtmfilingperiod >= '2020-01-01 00:00:00'
                                           and charities.customer_key is null
                                             group by --customer.flngcustomerkey
                                              Employees.fstrirdnumber
                                            -- , customer.fstrlistformatname
                                            -- , customer.fstrlistformataddress
                                            -- , customer.fstrtitle
                                             , EMPLOYER_IRD_NUMBER
                                             , EMPLOYEE_POST_CODE

CREATE TABLE lab_r3_assurance_project.SE_DAC
STORED AS PARQUET AS
select ird_number
, surname
, first_names
, from_timestamp(DOB, 'dd/MM/yyyy') as DOB
, max(mobile_phone) as mobile_phone
, post_code
, RTRIM(LTRIM(fstremail,' '),' ') AS EMAIL_ADDRESS
, entity_class
, trade_name
, 2019_inc as active_indicator
, sic_code
, sic_code_desc
, sic_grouping_level_1
, sic_grouping_level_2
, sic_grouping_level_3
, sic_grouping_level_4
from 
(SELECT 
a.ird_number as IRD_NUMBER, 
c.fstrfamilyname as SURNAME,  
concat(nvl(c.fstrfirstname, ''), ' ', nvl(c.fstrmiddlename, '')) as FIRST_NAMES,
c.fstrlistformataddress as ADDRESS, 
a.date_of_birth as DOB,
case when b.fstrPHONETYPE1 = 'CELL' AND b.fintCOUNTRYCODE1 = 64  THEN b.fstrPHONENUMBER1
when b.fstrPHONETYPE2 = 'CELL' AND b.fintCOUNTRYCODE2 = 64 THEN b.fstrPHONENUMBER2
when b.fstrPHONETYPE3 = 'CELL' AND b.fintCOUNTRYCODE3 = 64 THEN b.fstrPHONENUMBER3
when b.fstrPHONETYPE4 = 'CELL' AND b.fintCOUNTRYCODE4 = 64 THEN b.fstrPHONENUMBER4
when b.fstrPHONETYPE5 = 'CELL' AND b.fintCOUNTRYCODE5 = 64 THEN b.fstrPHONENUMBER5
end as MOBILE_PHONE,
w.fstremail,
c.fstrzip as POST_CODE, 
a.party_class_code as ENTITY_CLASS, 
nvl(a.trading_name,'') as TRADE_NAME,
a.bic_code as SIC_CODE, 
a.bic_desc as SIC_CODE_DESC, 
a.anzsic_level1_desc as SIC_GROUPING_LEVEL_1, 
a.anzsic_level2_desc as SIC_GROUPING_LEVEL_2, 
a.anzsic_level3_desc as SIC_GROUPING_LEVEL_3, 
a.anzsic_level4_desc as SIC_GROUPING_LEVEL_4,
case when (r.flngcustomerkey is not null or i.flngcustomerkey is not null) then 'Y' else 'N' end as 2019_INC,
case when a.party_class_code not in ('SW','CY','NR','OM','BO') then 'Y' else 'N' end as CLASS_CODE
from prod_refined_restricted_access.individual_dim a
inner join prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblcustomerinfo c 
on cast(a.customer_key as integer) = c.flngcustomerkey 
and  c.record_active_flag = 'Y'
left join prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblcontact b
on c.flngcustomerkey = b.flngcustomerkey
and b.record_active_flag = 'Y'
and b.flngver = 0
and b.fblnactive = 1
and (b.fstrPHONETYPE1 = 'CELL' or b.fstrPHONETYPE2 = 'CELL' or b.fstrPHONETYPE3 = 'CELL' or b.fstrPHONETYPE4 = 'CELL' or b.fstrPHONETYPE5 = 'CELL')

left join lab_r3_assurance_project.Owner_Email w
on w.flngcustomerkey = c.flngcustomerkey

left join 

(SELECT distinct (act.flngcustomerkey) as flngcustomerkey
FROM   prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblAccountInfo act 
INNER JOIN prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblReturn rtn 
ON         rtn.flngAccountKey    = act.flngAccountKey 
AND       act.fstrAccountType   ='IIT'
and rtn.flngVer           =0 
and rtn.record_active_flag = 'Y'
AND       rtn.fblnInError       =0 
AND       rtn.fstrStatus        ='RCVD' 
AND       rtn.fdtmFilingPeriod  = '2019-03-31 00:00:00'
inner join prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tbldocsetdoc dsd1 
ON rtn.fi64DocSetKey     =dsd1.fi64DocSetKey 
AND       dsd1.flngVer          =0 
and dsd1.record_active_flag = 'Y'
INNER JOIN prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblNZ_RtnAttributes att 
ON         rtn.flngDocKey        = att.flngDocKey
and att.fstrformtypefiled = '3'
and att.record_active_flag = 'Y'
inner JOIN prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblNz_RtnIit iit 
ON         dsd1.flngDocKey       = iit.flngDocKey 
WHERE     act.record_active_flag = 'Y'
AND       att.flngVer           =0
and (iit.fcurtotalactiveptshpincome <> 0.0000 or 
iit.fcurtotalactiveltcincome <> 0.0000 Or 
iit.fcurshareholderemployeesalary <> 0.0000 Or 
iit.fblnwithoutpayclosecompany <> 0.0000 OR
iit.fcurselfemployednetincome <> 0.0000 OR 
iit.fcurtotalothernetincome <> 0.0000
or iit.fcurtotalgrossschedularpayment <> 0.0000
or iit.fcurtotaloverseasincome <> 0)) r
on cast(a.customer_key as integer) = r.flngcustomerkey
left join prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblnz_income i 
on cast(a.customer_key as integer) = i.flngcustomerkey
and i.record_active_flag = 'Y'
and i.fdtmdate >= '2019-03-31 00:00:00'
and (i.fstrincometype in ('BUSINC','EXPNSE','OTHINC','PTRINC','SLFINC','OTHINC') or (i.fstrincometype in ('SHREMP','LTCINC','WT') and i.fcuramount <> 0))
where a.party_type = 'Individual' 
and a.record_active_flag = 'Y'
and c.flngcustomerkey != 0
and a.party_ceased_flag = 'N'
and a.emigrated_flag != 'Y'
and ird_number != 'Unknown'
) aa
where ird_number is not null
and (2019_inc = 'Y' or class_code = 'Y')


group by ird_number
, surname
, first_names
, DOB
, post_code
, email_address
, entity_class
, trade_name
, active_indicator
, sic_code
, sic_code_desc
, sic_grouping_level_1
, sic_grouping_level_2
, sic_grouping_level_3
, sic_grouping_level_4
